description:
Introducing the "Touhou Eiyashou Arrangements Pack Vol. 2" featuring various popular Tohou Eiyashou arrangements!
Including "Hirefuse Gumin-domo!" by IOSYS
and "Cruel CRuEL" by Diao ye zong!
You can now enjoy the long version of "Touhou Fushicho" 
by COSIO (ex ZUNTATA) exclusively for Spell Bubble!
Please enjoy this selection of great songs that are just as popular as Vol. 1!

#9th has joined as a new artist!

This pack contains the following:

■6 Songs
・Insect Night / ShinRa-Bansho
・Setsuna Yamai (feat. TINY PLANETS) / TamaOnSen
・Samidare no Starlight / #9th
・Cruel CRuEL / Diao ye zong
・Hirefuse Gumin-domo! / ARM + YOUNO Yoshimi (IOSYS) feat. Miko
・Touhou Fushicho / COSIO

■6 Challenge Stages
・Lv.5 Glitched Cirno! (Insect Night)
・Lv.6 Deputy General Manager Check (SetsunaYamai (feat.TINYPLANETS))
・Lv.7 Snacks in a Row (Samidare no Starlight)
・Lv.8 Ambivalent (Cruel CRuEL)
・Lv.9 Energy! Energy! (Hirefuse Gumin-domo!)
・Lv.10 Easily Bored (Touhou Fushicho)

* Internet connection required for purchase.
* Game must be restarted after songs are purchased in order to use them.
name: Touhou Eiyashou Arrangements Pack Vol.2
